// Parameters:			
//
// Return Value:		
//
// Changed On	By			Reason
// ----------	--------	-----------------------------------------------------------------------
// 21/07/2025	navdap1		Initial creation MTN-34430 MTN - Deferred Updates For Event Required For Login and Logout Trxs
